creator: Seedly
descriptionHtml:
We are Singapore’s first all-in-one personal finance app. Finally, there's a place to manage all your finances with ease. The best part - It’s FREE to use.

SEE EVERYTHING IN ONE PLACE
We bring together everything from account balances and expenses, to give you a full picture of your finances. There's no need to log into multiple sites or banking apps.

MANAGE YOUR EXPENSES
Set up a smart budget that tells you how much you can safely spend daily in two steps.

LEARN WITH US
We craft daily tips and advice for you to help you save, spend and invest smarter.

SAFE & SECURE
We take security very seriously and use measures like two-factor authentication (2FA), to protect your account. Seedly adheres to the same security encryption standards as your bank.

Over 60,000 users in Singapore trust us with their finances to provide them a clear and simple view of their money in one place.

WHY DO SINGAPOREANS CHOOSE SEEDLY?
• SG Budget Babe: My personal favourite expense tracking app? Seedly!
• Dollars & Sense: Recommended Personal Finance app
• TechInAsia: Simplify your personal finance app for millennials
• E27: This fintech startup wants to make personal finance management a breeze to millennials
• Vulcan Post: Experience in the DBS startup bootcamp
• NUS Enterprise and East Ventures Seed investors

HOW SEEDLY WORKS:
1. Simple: Designed with Singaporeans in mind, the interface is clutter-free and intuitive for the everyday user.

2. Smarter: We help you visualise and manage all your accounts in one place.

3. Secure: We adopt the latest mobile security standards in addition to security audits by experts in this field.

You can use Seedly manually or choose to sync and import transactions automatically from DBS, POSB, OCBC, UOB, Standard Chartered, Citibank, American Express (AMEX) banks and credit cards.
descriptionShort: Financial planning, expense tracking, personal asset management and community

title: Seedly - Expense Tracker & Budget App

creator: Seedly
descriptionHtml:
Seedly is a FREE personal finance app where you can read the latest money hacks & guides, discover & share investment ideas, discuss retirement-minded strategies, and track your expenses.

SEEDLY COMMUNITY: SHARE & DISCUSS PERSONAL FINANCE STRATEGIES
Seedly is Singapore’s largest personal finance community.

We are powered by the collective wisdom and diversity of experience of thousands of Seedly community members who connect daily to:
• discover and share new investment ideas and stock analysis
• discuss personal finance and retirement-minded strategies
• debate which credit card is the best
• make informed decisions on everything from insurance to mobile plans, and many more...

Join the conversation, gain insight, and achieve financial freedom!

BLOG ARTICLES: READ MONEY HACKS AND GUIDES
Dive into an unparalleled breadth and depth of personal finance-related topics: from investment guides, stocks analysis, and online brokerage reviews to maximising your CPF, choosing the best savings account, and saving for retirement.

We don’t sell anything so we promise that you’ll get well-researched and balanced perspectives.

EXPENSE TRACKER: SEE EVERYTHING AT A GLANCE
We bring together all of your bank accounts, credit cards, and expenses so you know exactly where you stand. Best of all? There’s no need to log in to multiple sites or banking apps. Just sync and import transactions from Amex, BOC, CIMB, Citibank, HSBC, OCBC, and UOB.

Alternatively, enjoy quick & easy manual expense entry in only 2 taps.

BUDGET MANAGEMENT: MANAGE YOUR MONEY LIKE A BOSS
Got a budget to stick to? Set up a monthly budget for all expenses or filter it by categories.

We’ll even tell you how much you can spend per day.

YOUR SECURITY, OUR PRIORITY
We take security very seriously and use measures like two-factor authentication (2FA) and asymmetric encryption to protect your account. We also adhere to the same security standards as your bank.

Our system has been designed to only parse and import financial data, which ONLY you can view. We cannot (and will NOT) manipulate any financial data or information.

Please visit Seedly to learn how we work to protect your privacy.
descriptionShort: Personal finance guides, stocks discussion, community, and expense tracking

descriptionHtml:
Seedly is a FREE personal finance app where you can read the latest money hacks & guides, discover & share investment ideas, discuss retirement-minded strategies, and track your expenses.

SEEDLY COMMUNITY: SHARE & DISCUSS PERSONAL FINANCE STRATEGIES
Seedly is Singapore’s largest personal finance community.

We are powered by the collective wisdom and diversity of experience of thousands of Seedly community members who connect daily to:
• discover and share new investment ideas and stock analysis
• discuss personal finance and retirement-minded strategies
• debate which credit card is the best
• make informed decisions on everything from insurance to mobile plans, and many more...

Join the conversation, gain insight, and achieve financial freedom!

BLOG ARTICLES: READ MONEY HACKS AND GUIDES
Dive into an unparalleled breadth and depth of personal finance-related topics: from investment guides, stocks analysis, and online brokerage reviews to maximising your CPF, choosing the best savings account, and saving for retirement.

We don’t sell anything so we promise that you’ll get well-researched and balanced perspectives.

EXPENSE TRACKER: SEE EVERYTHING AT A GLANCE
We bring together all of your bank accounts, credit cards, and expenses so you know exactly where you stand. Best of all? There’s no need to log in to multiple sites or banking apps. Just sync and import transactions from Amex, BOC, CIMB, Citibank, HSBC, OCBC, and UOB.

Alternatively, enjoy quick & easy manual expense entry in only 2 taps.

BUDGET MANAGEMENT: MANAGE YOUR MONEY LIKE A BOSS
Got a budget to stick to? Set up a monthly budget for all expenses or filter it by categories.

We’ll even tell you how much you can spend per day.

YOUR SECURITY, OUR PRIORITY
We take security very seriously and use measures like two-factor authentication (2FA) and asymmetric encryption to protect your account. We also adhere to the same security standards as your bank.

Our system has been designed to only parse and import financial data, which ONLY you can view. We cannot (and will NOT) manipulate any financial data or information.

Please visit Seedly to learn how we work to protect your privacy.
descriptionShort: Personal finance guides, stocks discussion, community, and expense tracking

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
This update includes bug fixes and performance improvements.

We're always open to your suggestions on how to improve, so if you've got any (or wanna say hi!), drop us a message at support@seedly.sg!
